# HighRise Design Token Rules

## Token Structure Cleanup Guidelines

### Schema and Metadata Removal
- **Remove all schema/metadata**: $schema, $description, name, version, description
- **Use actual component name as root key** (e.g., "input", "button", "tag-count") not "component"
- **Remove documentation sections**: responsive, states, variants, types
- **Keep only core token definitions**: size, color, border-radius, container

### Token Hierarchy Workflow
**CRITICAL**: Always follow this hierarchy:
1. **Check primitive tokens first** - if value doesn't exist, add to primitive tokens
2. **Add to semantic tokens** - create semantic reference to primitive
3. **Reference in component tokens** - use semantic token reference
4. **Never create arbitrary values** - all values must flow through primitive → semantic → component

### Token Reference Patterns (NO "semantic." PREFIX)

#### Colors (use actual primitive structure)
- Primary colors: `{color.primary.blue.600}` (not color.brand.primary)
- Status colors: `{color.secondary.error}`, `{color.secondary.warning}`, `{color.secondary.success}` (not color.status.*)
- Neutral colors: `{color.neutral.gray.100}`, `{color.neutral.gray.700}`
- Background: `{color.background.neutral.subtle.1}`
- Text: `{color.text.neutral.body.1}`
- Border: `{color.border.neutral.default}`

#### Transparent Values - ALWAYS Use Semantic Tokens
- **NEVER use raw "transparent"** - always use semantic token reference
- Background transparent: `{color.background.transparent}`
- Border transparent: `{color.border.transparent}`
- Text transparent: `{color.text.transparent}`
- Icon transparent: `{color.icon.transparent}`

#### Border Radius (use actual primitive structure)
- Border radius: `{border.radius.0[5]}`, `{border.radius.1}`, `{border.radius.2}` (not size.width.*)
- Circular borders: `{border.radius.full}` (not specific values)

#### Spacing References (NO "tokens." PREFIX)
**Default approach**: Use direct semantic tokens without unnecessary prefixes
- **Padding tokens**: `{padding.0[75]}`, `{padding.1}`, `{padding.1[25]}`, `{padding.1[5]}`, `{padding.1[75]}`, `{padding.2}`, `{padding.2[5]}`, `{padding.3}`, etc.
- **Size tokens**: `{size.4}`, `{size.5}`, `{size.6}`, `{size.7}`, `{size.8}`, `{size.9}`, `{size.10}`, `{size.11}`, `{size.12}`, `{size.14}`, `{size.16}`, etc.
- **Use directional tokens only when needed**: `{padding.x.xs}`, `{padding.y.sm}`, `{gap.x.md}`, etc. for components requiring specific directional spacing
- **NEVER use "tokens.padding.x" or "tokens.gap.x"** - always use direct references
- **Format fractional values as 0[5] not 0.5** - they are at the same level

#### Size Optimization
- **When width and height are same, use single size token**: `{size.1}`, `{size.xs}`, `{size.sm}`, `{size.md}`, `{size.lg}`, `{size.xl}`, `{size.2xl}`
- **For icon sizes, use semantic**: `{size.icon.4xs}`, `{size.icon.3xs}`, `{size.icon.2xs}`, `{size.icon.xs}`, `{size.icon.sm}`, `{size.icon.md}`, `{size.icon.lg}`, `{size.icon.xl}`, `{size.icon.2xl}`, `{size.icon.3xl}`, `{size.icon.4xl}`
- **Use numeric**: `{size.1}`, `{size.2}`, `{size.3}`, etc. for basic dimensions

#### Semantic Token Precision
- **Be precise with semantic levels**: Use exact level numbers (0, 1, 2) based on actual design intent
- **Subtle levels**: `subtle.0` (lightest), `subtle.1` (light), `subtle.2` (medium light)
- **Moderate levels**: `moderate.0`, `moderate.1`, `moderate.2`, `moderate.3`
- **Intense levels**: `intense.0`, `intense.1`, `intense.2`
- **Don't default to level 2** - choose the appropriate level for the specific use case

#### Spacing References (available when directional specificity needed)
**PADDING:**
- General: `{padding.0}`, `{padding.1}`, `{padding.2}`, etc.
- Horizontal: `{padding.x.0}`, `{padding.x.1}`, `{padding.x.xs}`, `{padding.x.sm}`, `{padding.x.md}`, `{padding.x.lg}`, `{padding.x.xl}`, `{padding.x.2xl}`
- Vertical: `{padding.y.0}`, `{padding.y.1}`, `{padding.y.xs}`, `{padding.y.sm}`, `{padding.y.md}`, `{padding.y.lg}`, `{padding.y.xl}`, `{padding.y.2xl}`

**MARGIN:**
- General: `{margin.0}`, `{margin.1}`, `{margin.2}`, etc.
- Horizontal: `{margin.x.0}`, `{margin.x.1}`, `{margin.x.xs}`, `{margin.x.sm}`, `{margin.x.md}`, `{margin.x.lg}`, `{margin.x.xl}`, `{margin.x.2xl}`
- Vertical: `{margin.y.0}`, `{margin.y.1}`, `{margin.y.xs}`, `{margin.y.sm}`, `{margin.y.md}`, `{margin.y.lg}`, `{margin.y.xl}`, `{margin.y.2xl}`
- Directional: `{margin.top.*}`, `{margin.right.*}`, `{margin.bottom.*}`, `{margin.left.*}`

**GAP:**
- General: `{gap.0}`, `{gap.1}`, `{gap.2}`, etc.
- Horizontal: `{gap.x.0}`, `{gap.x.1}`, `{gap.x.xs}`, `{gap.x.sm}`, `{gap.x.md}`, `{gap.x.lg}`, `{gap.x.xl}`, `{gap.x.2xl}`
- Vertical: `{gap.y.0}`, `{gap.y.1}`, `{gap.y.xs}`, `{gap.y.sm}`, `{gap.y.md}`, `{gap.y.lg}`, `{gap.y.xl}`, `{gap.y.2xl}`
- Semantic: `{gap.x.3xs}`, `{gap.x.2xs}`, `{gap.x.xs}`, `{gap.x.sm}`, `{gap.x.md}`, `{gap.x.lg}`, `{gap.x.xl}`, `{gap.x.2xl}`
- Between: `{gap.x.between.3xs}`, `{gap.x.between.2xs}`, `{gap.x.between.xs}`, etc.
- Negative values: `{gap.-1}`, `{gap.-2}`, `{gap.x.-1}`, `{gap.y.-1}`

**POSITION:**
- General: `{position.0}`, `{position.1}`, `{position.2}`, `{position.0[5]}`, `{position.1[5]}`, etc.
- Horizontal: `{position.x.0}`, `{position.x.1}`, `{position.x.0[5]}`, `{position.x.0[25]}`, `{position.x.0[75]}`, etc.
- Vertical: `{position.y.0}`, `{position.y.1}`, `{position.y.0[5]}`, `{position.y.0[25]}`, `{position.y.0[75]}`, etc.
- Negative values: `{position.-1}`, `{position.-0[5]}`, `{position.x.-1}`, `{position.y.-1}`, etc.

#### Typography References
- **Font tokens**: `{font.body.medium.2xs}`, `{font.body.medium.xs}`, `{font.body.medium.sm}`, `{font.body.medium.md}`
- **Use complete typography tokens**: Include size, weight, and line-height
- **Component typography pattern**:
  ```json
  "text": {
    "typography": {
      "xs": {"value": "{font.body.medium.xs}", "type": "string"},
      "sm": {"value": "{font.body.medium.sm}", "type": "string"},
      "md": {"value": "{font.body.medium.md}", "type": "string"},
      "lg": {"value": "{font.body.medium.md}", "type": "string"}
    }
  }
  ```
- **Separate from color variants**: Typography is usually consistent across color variants

### Fractional Value Format
- **Use bracket notation for fractions**: `0[5]` for 0.5, `1[25]` for 1.25, `1[5]` for 1.5, `1[75]` for 1.75, etc.
- **Fractional tokens are at same level as whole numbers**: `{padding.0[5]}`, `{padding.1}`, `{padding.1[25]}` are all direct siblings

### Component Context Clarity
- **Each component has its own spacing context and purpose**
- **Use direct tokens as default, directional tokens only when component requires specific axis control**
- **Component token descriptions should reflect the actual usage context**

## Component Structural Patterns

### Pattern 1: Shared/Variants Structure (PREFERRED)
**Best for**: Form components, interactive elements with consistent structure across color variants
**Examples**: input, button, tag, textarea

```json
{
  "component-name": {
    "shared": {
      "border": {
        "radius": {
          "value": "{border.radius.sm}",
          "type": "dimension"
        },
        "width": {
          "value": "{border.width.default}",
          "type": "dimension"
        }
      },
      "padding": {
        "x": {
          "value": "{padding.xs}",
          "type": "dimension"
        },
        "y": {
          "value": "{padding.2xs}",
          "type": "dimension"
        }
      },
      "height": {
        "xs": {
          "value": "{size.height.xs}",
          "type": "dimension"
        },
        "sm": {
          "value": "{size.height.sm}",
          "type": "dimension"
        },
        "md": {
          "value": "{size.height.md}",
          "type": "dimension"
        },
        "lg": {
          "value": "{size.height.lg}",
          "type": "dimension"
        }
      },
      "min-width": {
        "value": "{size.width.64}",
        "type": "dimension"
      }
    },
    "text": {
      "typography": {
        "xs": {"value": "{font.body.regular.xs}", "type": "string"},
        "sm": {"value": "{font.body.regular.sm}", "type": "string"},
        "md": {"value": "{font.body.regular.md}", "type": "string"},
        "lg": {"value": "{font.body.regular.base}", "type": "string"}
      }
    },
    "icon": {
      "size": {
        "xs": {"value": "{size.icon.xs}", "type": "dimension"},
        "sm": {"value": "{size.icon.xs}", "type": "dimension"},
        "md": {"value": "{size.icon.sm}", "type": "dimension"},
        "lg": {"value": "{size.icon.md}", "type": "dimension"}
      }
    },
    "variants": {
      "neutral": {
        "default": {
          "background": {
            "default": {"value": "{color.background.neutral.base}", "type": "color"},
            "hover": {"value": "{color.background.neutral.base}", "type": "color"},
            "active": {"value": "{color.background.neutral.base}", "type": "color"},
            "focused": {"value": "{color.background.neutral.base}", "type": "color"},
            "disabled": {"value": "{color.background.neutral.subtle.0}", "type": "color"}
          },
          "border": {
            "default": {"value": "{color.border.neutral.default}", "type": "color"},
            "hover": {"value": "{color.border.primary.default}", "type": "color"},
            "active": {"value": "{color.border.primary.default}", "type": "color"},
            "focused": {"value": "{color.border.primary.default}", "type": "color"},
            "disabled": {"value": "{color.border.neutral.default}", "type": "color"}
          },
          "text": {
            "default": {"value": "{color.text.neutral.subtitle.1}", "type": "color"},
            "hover": {"value": "{color.text.neutral.subtitle.1}", "type": "color"},
            "active": {"value": "{color.text.neutral.title.1}", "type": "color"},
            "focused": {"value": "{color.text.neutral.title.1}", "type": "color"},
            "disabled": {"value": "{color.text.neutral.subtitle.2}", "type": "color"},
            "placeholder": {"value": "{color.text.neutral.subtitle.1}", "type": "color"}
          },
          "icon": {
            "default": {"value": "{color.icon.neutral.info}", "type": "color"},
            "hover": {"value": "{color.icon.neutral.info}", "type": "color"},
            "active": {"value": "{color.icon.neutral.info}", "type": "color"},
            "focused": {"value": "{color.icon.neutral.info}", "type": "color"},
            "disabled": {"value": "{color.icon.neutral.subtle.2}", "type": "color"}
          },
          "focus": {
            "ring": {"value": "{color.border.primary.subtle.2}", "type": "color"},
            "shadow": {"value": "0px 0px 0px 4px rgba(209, 224, 255, 1), 0px 1px 2px 0px rgba(16, 24, 40, 0.05)", "type": "boxShadow"}
          }
        }
      },
      "primary": {
        "default": {
          // Same structure as neutral
        }
      },
      "error": {
        "default": {
          // Same structure as neutral
        }
      }
    }
  }
}
```

### Pattern 2: Container-Based Structure
**Best for**: Simple components without complex color variants, utility components
**Examples**: checkbox, select, avatar (when color variation is minimal)

```json
{
  "component-name": {
    "container": {
      "size": {
        "xs": {"value": "{size.3}", "type": "dimension"},
        "sm": {"value": "{size.4}", "type": "dimension"},
        "md": {"value": "{size.5}", "type": "dimension"},
        "lg": {"value": "{size.6}", "type": "dimension"}
      },
      "border": {
        "radius": {
          "xs": {"value": "{border.radius.1}", "type": "dimension"},
          "sm": {"value": "{border.radius.1}", "type": "dimension"},
          "md": {"value": "{border.radius.1[5]}", "type": "dimension"},
          "lg": {"value": "{border.radius.2}", "type": "dimension"}
        },
        "width": {"value": "{border.width.default}", "type": "dimension"}
      },
      "background": {
        "default": {"value": "{color.background.neutral.base}", "type": "color"},
        "hover": {"value": "{color.background.primary.subtle.1}", "type": "color"},
        "focused": {"value": "{color.background.neutral.base}", "type": "color"},
        "disabled": {"value": "{color.background.neutral.subtle.1}", "type": "color"}
      },
      "border-color": {
        "default": {"value": "{color.border.neutral.default}", "type": "color"},
        "hover": {"value": "{color.border.primary.default}", "type": "color"},
        "focused": {"value": "{color.border.primary.default}", "type": "color"},
        "disabled": {"value": "{color.border.neutral.subtle.1}", "type": "color"}
      }
    }
  }
}
```

